### create chat

POST http://localhost:6688/api/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "acme",
    "members": [1,2],
    "public": false
}

### get chat list

GET http://localhost:6688/api/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}

### delete chat

DELETE http://localhost:6688/api/chats/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}


### get user list

